3 will it be foggy in the next two_days ?	the next two_days will be foggy , one will be foggy with a low of 50f and a high of 70f and the other will be raining , low of 90f with a high of 100f
4 thanks	not a problem

3 will it be blizzard in the next two_days ?	the next two_days will be blizzard , one will be blizzard with a low of 40f and a high of 50f and the other will be drizzle , low of 60f with a high of 80f
4 thanks	not a problem
